summary:
When she is captured by 'that cunt', he never said anything for days. He just hammered. He made hard songs with his hammer.
But...
body:
When she is captured by ‘that cunt’, he never said anything for days. He just hammered. He made hard songs with his hammer.

But then they talked about her. 'Not with his side’.They knew he was felt bad about that.

She was in Winterfell… He smiled until he heard his name. 'with Ramsay Bolton’.

She was married with Ramsay Bolton. 'But it is impossible.She is not a lady. At least not like that one.’

But it wasn’t important. She didn’t have anybody with her. Her family is dead and her friends left her too. She is 'no one’ but a prisoner for them. 'a precious one but still a prisoner’.

Not for him.

When he thought her in that bastard’s bed he was hammering. He was making a hard song with his hammer.

Gendry x Arya
